    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it's spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
